The cold of the first month is dissipating and February is warming up. Spring 2020 may be a little late, but we believe she will be there.

During the outbreak, Bai Hualin has been helping patients around the closed management and faced with drug withdrawal to coordinate medication, the online platform to share the story of AI friend has also been many people's resonance and Response. Voice, sometimes represents a force, and Birchwood is for the vast number of AIDS patients in a brave voice, so that society can hear from this special corner of the demand.

The hero of today's story comes from the Karamay in Xinjiang, which I'll call him, for now, Xiaowei.

Karamay, Xinjiang

Speaking of Xinjiang, I do not know if you and I feel the same, distance and strange feeling inadvertently mixed with a trace of fear. Living in a small town in the eastern part of the motherland, I have never set foot in the great rivers and mountains of the western regions, and I have no friends from Xinjiang by my side. I know very little about the local conditions and customs, plus the religious atmosphere there, i also have never seen the world to think that the mysterious land of Ai you may be more difficult than I live it.

Wei, who works in Chongqing, was off his meds when he got in touch with Betula Platyphylla. Originally intended to fly back from Urumqi to Chongqing to obtain medicine, but encountered the epidemic closed, suddenly no idea, panic to the extreme. Ms. Betula Platyphylla had asked many of the people who had borrowed drugs for help. They said the feeling was hopelessness, a level of hopelessness that was tempered by the knowledge that the worst was already in place. It's more a matter of luck to post, ask for help, or ask volunteers for help. After all, the combination of drugs may be different for people you don't know. Plus, everyone has a limited supply of drugs. How can you borrow so easily?

During the outbreak, closed management is strict, for usually take medicine time is very cautious to guard Xiaowei, the blow can be imagined. In his many years of volunteering, Bai Hua has placed more than 14,000 tags on his phone, creating a vast grid that spans the country and the world, and this net did not know how many help in the despair of ai you. This time, very lucky, white birch forest and for the body in Xinjiang Xiaowei found that Lucky "point. ".

A-feng saw Pu Shu's message in the group and contacted us immediately, saying that he could help Xiaowei through the difficult times. I have always believed that there will be a fate between people, Difficult Times in the benefactor do not know when the nature. A Feng is a doctor with city access, and although he is already taking self-financed drugs, he still has a free Tirai mix he can lend to Xiao Wei. We are all happy for Xiao Wei. Teacher Betula Platyphylla said, do so many years of AIDS support work, the greatest happiness may be this moment! The vast sea, people in prison longing for that boat, today you cross me, perhaps one day I will give you a ride, this is not the first heart of Birch forest?

![img](data:image/jpeg;base64,)
Medicine is life, the post is too late, we discuss with the next day to the medicine directly to Xiaowei residential area, a Feng agreed. Then, Xiao Wei called and told us the good news. After negotiation, the neighborhood committee agreed that he could leave the closed community and go to the airport, but only on his own. His family and relatives could not accompany him. Karamay is a long way from Urumqi's airport, and the lack of transport is certainly unrealistic. Betula Platyphylla again communicated with a Feng, whether in the delivery of medicine and then sent Xiaowei to the airport, as soon as possible to return to Chongqing, so as not to The Big Sleep. This time, ah fung readily agreed.

Listening to Betula Platyphylla share this story, I haven't had any communication with Ah Feng in the story so far, but I really admire him, thank him, if there is a chance, I would like to see him. To be able to offer unconditional help to a stranger I've never met, I would say that this giving gives me a sense of hope that comes from the power of looking out for each other.

A Feng smoothly received Xiaowei, and provided him with enough transitional medicine, Xiaowei also flew back from Xinjiang to Chongqing. I am thinking, this perplexity may let Xiaowei more firmly the hope of life, and A-feng will also try to cherish the happiness of possession. The Bible says, "be glad for many years if you live long, but think of the dark days, for they will be many, and all that will come will be vanity. ". We have experienced many ups and downs along the way, confused and desperate, but as long as we see the truth of life, and earnestly strive to go on, what can break us?

![img](data:image/jpeg;base64,)
Several late-night talk with White Birch Teacher Wechat, can see that he is very tired, because of the pile of pieces, but it is about life, so he can not give up easily. Limited resources can also become even more inadequate when faced with an ever-increasing number of demand groups. I often think, if there is no mutual understanding, I am afraid that any existence will become fleeting. So no matter where you are, what you've been through, or what you've been through, cherish the opportunity and the opportunity to be each other.

Today's story is not complicated, the plot is not soul-stirring, and in this human nature, the virus wanton of the bizarre, it gives us the trust, understanding and unity of enlightenment. Each of us with AIDS, are unable to leave this society and achieve complete solitude, looking for life in the connection, love and hope may make life not so hard!
